race.comment: Tough race but sticking with PIN DEEP (1) who is in great form. Runner-up second-up then was a big four-length winner at Northam with a big weight. Carries 1kg more but in-form claimer is back aboard and off the low draw will take catching again. MAGALI MAGIC (6) was a Northam winner two back then just missed over 1200m at Belmont Park. Drawn for a soft run with cover and will be angling for runs late. THIS'LL SHOW YA (7) was a forgive run behind PIN DEEP at Northam last time when she ran well off best. Previous form was sound and on good record here can bounce back. JUST SAINT JAMES (3) resumes on the back of two trials and has won fresh. Parnham has had five rides for two wins and three minors while aboard. MIGHTY HOSANNA (8) presents on the back of a trial and is a speedy mare resuming. Will push forward and give a sight.
